metadata.name: -CONSUME-
metadata.description:
According to research we are exposed to over 6000 adverts a day and it is now easier than ever for companies to target consumers with tailored ads. 

We live in a constant loop of being fed fast food while being shamed into being skinny. Of being told we need to buy the latest gadgets, while being ridiculed for not saving our money.

Corporations have preyed on consumers using this model for years... Will you break out of the loop?
